  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the robata-grill to 400°F (200°C).",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together coconut milk, honey, lime juice, ginger paste, and galangal paste.",
    "Add the sliced Polish sausage to the marinade and mix well.",
    "Cover the bowl with plastic wrap and refrigerate for at least 30 minutes or up to 2 hours.",
    "Thread the marinated sausage onto pre-soaked bamboo skewers, leaving a little space between each piece.",
    "Brush the robata-grill with robata-grill oil to prevent sticking.",
    "Grill the satay for 8-10 minutes on each side, or until nicely charred and cooked through.",
    "Serve immediately, garnished with chopped peanuts and cilantro, with cilantro-lime sauce on the side if desired.",
    "Optional: serve with steamed jasmine rice or roti for a more filling meal."
  ],
